<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.11">
<l>āṭkoḷḷat tōṉṟiya vāyartaṅ kōviṉai</l>
<l>nāṭkamaḻ pūmpoḻil villiput tūrppaṭṭaṉ</l>
<l>vēṭkaiyāṟ coṉṉa cappāṇi yīraintum</l>
<l>vēṭkaiyi ṉāṟcollu vārviṉai pōmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The karma of those who speak with desire the ten cappāṇi [verses]</l>
<l>that were spoken with desire by the scholar of Villiputtūr</l>
<l rend="indent">with gardens that bloom, emiting fragrance daily,</l>
<l>about the king of the cowherds who appeared in order to grasp [his] servants,</l>
<l>will depart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
